# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:14
translate chinese maris6_be3f6d99:

    # fr "Hrm, that's an interesting question."
    fr "嗯，这真是个有趣的问题。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:16
translate chinese maris6_ef72eb58:

    # fr "I like being a woman."
    fr "我喜欢做女人。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:17
translate chinese maris6_0d872a23:

    # fr "But men do tend to underestimate me."
    fr "但男人确实总爱低估我。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:18
translate chinese maris6_f702735f:

    # fr "They look at me and think that I'm weak, that I need their protection, or that I need somebody to save me from this difficult life."
    fr "他们看着我就觉得我很软弱，觉得我需要他们的保护，或者觉得我需要有人把我从这艰难的生活中拯救出来。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:19
translate chinese maris6_7b7ee184:

    # fr "I like my life though."
    fr "不过，我喜欢我的生活。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:20
translate chinese maris6_50820c07:

    # fr "I love my farm and my animals."
    fr "我热爱我的农场和我的动物们。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:21
translate chinese maris6_0a17b87a:

    # fr "I like to see their faces when I show them how strong I am, that I do this whole farm on my own plus work two jobs and go to school."
    fr "我喜欢看到她们脸上惊讶的表情，当我向她们展示我有多坚强——我独自打理整个农场，同时还要打两份工并上学。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:23
translate chinese maris6_97816180:

    # fr "I don't need any help from a man."
    fr "我不需要男人的任何帮助。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris6.rpy:24
translate chinese maris6_979c7349:

    # fr "The only thing I want from a man is love and attention."
    fr "我唯一想要的，是男人的爱和关注。"

